WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:04.537 --> 00:00:05.972
Mother Water,

00:00:06.005 --> 00:00:07.906
when they destroy the lakes,

00:00:07.940 --> 00:00:10.110
where will their owners go...

00:00:11.277 --> 00:00:13.546
the spirits of the lakes?

00:00:29.595 --> 00:00:30.729
Daughter of the Lake

00:00:30.763 --> 00:00:34.000
Tell me about the
problems you're having.

00:00:34.033 --> 00:00:36.002
The mining company
won't let me live in peace.

00:00:36.035 --> 00:00:38.705
They say there is gold
under my land.

00:00:38.738 --> 00:00:43.109
It's greed for gold that makes them
want to take my land by force.

00:00:43.143 --> 00:00:44.643
Maxima, Maxima

00:00:44.677 --> 00:00:47.514
If you haven't sold it,
you're still the owner.

00:00:49.482 --> 00:00:51.183
Mother Water,

00:00:51.217 --> 00:00:55.055
don't they understand
 that you're a living being?

00:00:59.158 --> 00:01:03.096
Now I've been studying law
 for 5 years.

00:01:05.231 --> 00:01:07.467
We'll get justice.

00:01:08.734 --> 00:01:13.072
Mom, you know what I miss
when I'm in the city?

00:01:13.105 --> 00:01:15.208
I miss my animals.

00:01:16.208 --> 00:01:18.711
Life isn't good in the city.

00:01:19.912 --> 00:01:22.449
I want to finish my studies
and come back.

00:01:25.385 --> 00:01:28.788
They told me if you and I
are in the protests,

00:01:28.821 --> 00:01:30.657
then there's no work for me.

00:01:30.690 --> 00:01:32.158
And you believed them?

00:01:32.759 --> 00:01:33.259
Yes

00:01:34.393 --> 00:01:37.363
How has this incident happened?

00:01:37.397 --> 00:01:40.065
They came into my land
 with their guns...

00:01:40.099 --> 00:01:42.368
Thugs sent by
 the mining company.

00:01:43.970 --> 00:01:45.438
Mother Water,

00:01:46.405 --> 00:01:49.576
there is gold deep inside you.

00:01:52.445 --> 00:01:55.181
Blood is spilled for gold.

00:01:56.182 --> 00:01:59.886
You can't drink gold.
 You can't eat gold.

00:02:04.857 --> 00:02:07.827
We're at the Conga lakes,

00:02:07.860 --> 00:02:09.395
there are policemen here.

00:02:09.429 --> 00:02:12.866
They seem ready to attack
and evict us.

00:02:15.568 --> 00:02:17.069
Mother Water,

00:02:17.102 --> 00:02:19.672
I'm afraid for my life.

